kandi wenda nyogokuru azi gukora imishinga neza

200
00:11:38,408 --> 00:11:39,796
aho byaba ari byiza.

201
00:11:39,797 --> 00:11:45,143
ashobora kukugira inama z'uburyo wakuza umushinga wawe.

202
00:11:45,179 --> 00:11:48,882
ariko inshuro nyinshi, inshuti zawe
n'umuryango wawe

203
00:11:48,883 --> 00:11:51,818
ntabwo bazashobora kukugira inama ku bijyanye n'umushinga wawe.

204
00:11:51,819 --> 00:11:53,429
rero, nkuko mubibona.

205
00:11:53,430 --> 00:11:59,234
hari uruhande rw'ibibi byinshi byo gukorana n'imiryango n'inshuti,

206
00:11:59,235 --> 00:12:01,327
bivanze n'ibindi byiza byinshi.

207
00:12:01,328 --> 00:12:04,748
Ubu tumaze kumenya iby'ingenzi mu isomo ryacu

208
00:12:04,749 --> 00:12:08,546
ku bijyanye no gukusanya inkunga,
n'uburyo bwo gutangiza no gukora umushinga

209
00:12:08,547 --> 00:12:12,787
dufite ikifuzo cyo gukusanya inkunga ku kibaho cyacu.

210
00:12:13,798 --> 00:12:16,297
