nk'amafaranga ya mbere yo gutangiza umushinga

213
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:23,499
nkuko uba uhamagarira abantu gutanga inkunga,

214
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:27,249
nibwo utangira kubishyira ku mbuga zitandukanye kuri interineti

215
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:31,155
kandi akenshi uyaka n'abantu mutaziranye.

216
00:12:32,601 --> 00:12:34,847
akenshi, iba ari impano,

217
00:12:35,934 --> 00:12:39,558
