224
00:12:57,849 --> 00:12:59,546
ku bashoramari baguteye inkunga.

225
00:13:01,401 --> 00:13:04,972
akenshi umubare w'amafaranga uba uri ku rugero rw'igihumbi

226
00:13:04,973 --> 00:13:08,996
kugeza ku bihumbi ijana,
ndavuga inshuro ebyiri ku musaruro wa buri muntu,

227
00:13:09,113 --> 00:13:14,633
ariko amafaranga ni make cyane, ku kigereranyo cya 7,000.

228
00:13:17,246 --> 00:13:19,212
