uretseko, ikintu kimwe tubona ni ubwigenge,

602
00:34:23,212 --> 00:34:27,955
ni byibanze kugumana ubuyobozi igihe cyose ubonye imfashanyo cyangwa impano.

603
00:34:28,975 --> 00:34:33,512
nibyo byibanze bitanu kuberako ibi bibabirimo

604
00:34:33,513 --> 00:34:37,391
Imfashanyo, inguzanyo, nimpano.

605
00:34:37,393 --> 00:34:39,625
bityo, nturimo uragurisha imigabane

606
00:34:42,487 --> 00:34:45,906
muburyo bwo gutera inkunga, twari twavuze kumubare wamafaranga.

607
00:34:46,917 --> 00:34:49,143
ntuzabona umusaruro mwinci.

608
00:34:49,712 --> 00:34:54,851
kandi twabivuzeho, niwubuka byazaba bibi nutabishyira mubikorwa..

609
00:34:54,851 --> 00:34:56,909
muyandi magambo, kumenyekana nibyiza.

610
00:34:56,911 --> 00:35:00,903
ushobora kuzigama ko wakira amafaranga kunkunga.

611
00:35:00,904 --> 00:35:04,318
ariko, byumwihariko, iyo ugurisha mbere, itonde

612
00:35:04,319 --> 00:35:09,160
kuberako nudategura neza, bishobora kubangamira imenyekana ryawe.

613
00:35:10,322 --> 00:35:14,398
kuri banki, ikintu kibanze hano  nuko imara amafaranga yawe.

614
00:35:17,482 --> 00:35:19,681
uri mukibazo cyo kwishyura inguzanyanyo. 

615
00:35:20,105 --> 00:35:23,789
kurundi ruhande bibaho kubera imiyoborere.

616
00:35:23,790 --> 00:35:25,995
bisobanuye ko iyo utsinze ubona inguzanyo

617
00:35:25,996 --> 00:35:28,864
ibyo bisobanura ko bemera ko uzagira

618
00:35:28,865 --> 00:35:30,235
umushinga wagahebuzo.

619
00:35:30,949 --> 00:35:32,822
nibyiza kwisura yawe.

620
00:35:33,244 --> 00:35:37,111
Fondasiyo, ikibazo kini hano ni igihe bifata

621
00:35:37,112 --> 00:35:38,741
gukusanya amafaranga ya fondasiyo.

622
00:35:38,742 --> 00:35:43,800
amezi atatu kugeza kuri atandatu nigihe cyirekire mubuzima bwa kompanyi itangira. 
 

623
00:35:45,164 --> 00:35:48,460
kandi ugomba gushaka umuryango ufite misiyo isa. 

624
00:35:49,206 --> 00:35:53,457
amarushanwa yogutangira ninama nziza cyane.

625
00:35:53,458 --> 00:35:56,148
nutsinda, ubone icyubahiro cyinci.

626
00:35:56,149 --> 00:35:58,098
byiza kwimenyekana ryawe.

627
00:35:58,099 --> 00:36:02,965
ikibi, urimo kwamamaza ibyo ukora

628
00:36:02,966 --> 00:36:04,966
Kwisi hose.

629
00:36:06,305 --> 00:36:13,015
nyuma nanyuma, hamwe nabashoramari ushobora kubona umusaruro.

630
00:36:13,615 --> 00:36:17,833
nibyingenzi utangira amafaranga,

631
00:36:17,834 --> 00:36:19,606
bifitanye isano cyane nikigitekerezo 

632
00:36:19,607 --> 00:36:24,383
ko ugomba kureka ubuyobozi bumwe nabumwe bwumushinga wawe.

633
00:36:24,384 --> 00:36:27,009
subuyubozi bwose kuko abashoramari benshi

634
00:36:27,010 --> 00:36:32,086
ntibafata umushinga wawe cyangwa ngo imigabane.

635
00:36:32,087 --> 00:36:35,141
ariko, ugiye kunanirwa kuyobora bimwe.

636
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:37,882
kurundi ruhande, ntibazakuba ingwate,

637
00:36:37,883 --> 00:36:41,613
ugiye kubasha gukoresha amafaranga neza.

638
00:36:41,614 --> 00:36:44,973
reka ubu turebe kurugero rwimbuto namafaranga yo gutangira.

639
00:36:44,974 --> 00:36:49,728
nuko tuzareba neza, nyuma gato mugihembwe gikurikiyeho.

640
00:36:49,729 --> 00:36:52,626
bijyanye no guzamuka no kwiyongera kwamafaranga.

641
00:36:52,627 --> 00:36:53,636
murakoze cyane.
